Dinner Party / Banquet Package
/$
$
There is NO CHARGE for the venue rental with the purchase of a Party Package
Linens, choice of napkin colors, uplighting, centerpieces, china and dinnerware are ALL included
All catering services are included - Open Bar, appetizers, salad, dinner, and dessert
All Packages include four hours of the event space, our complete set-up and tear-down, plus all of the following:
BEVERAGES
One Hour of Full Open Bar - upon arrival, prior to beginning of food service
OR
Four Hours Open Draft Beer and House Wines
​
​
​
HORS D’OEUVRES
–
Choose any three
​
Bacon Wrapped Scallops  -  Fried Shrimp  -  BBQ Meatballs  -  Mini Pizzas
Mini Chicken Cordon Bleu  -  Chicken Tenders
Egg Rolls  -  Franks in Puff Pastry  -  Cheese and Cracker Tray
Fruit Tray  -  Antipasto Tray  -  Vegetable and Dip Tray

–
Choose one
Garden Salad  -  Cucumber Salad  -  Tomato Vinaigrette
Pasta Salad  -  Potato Salad  -  Caesar Salad
ENTRÉE
– 3 Selection Buffet -
See Buffet Menu for Choices
VEGETABLE

Vegetable Medley  -  Snow Peas with Mushrooms  -  Mexicorn
Broiled Tomato Halves w/ Parmesan  -  Baby Carrots
STARCH

Rice Pilaf  -  Baked Potatoes  -  White or Yellow Rice  -  Roasted Potatoes
Linguine Marinara  -  Scalloped Potatoes  -  Garlic Mashed Potatoes
COFFEE AND DESSERT STATION AFTER DINNER
$49.95 per person
- 40 guest minimum please 150 guest maximum -
